HEADWORD: Perula
<hw>Per"u*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Perul⟦ae⟧</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., dim. of
